StringValues.16: A letter of introduction, addressed to Jilsaya bint Dah in al-Arqas from Sarqah bint Ak in the North Outpost.
StringValues.15: A letter of introduction, addressed to Jilsaya bint Dah from Sarqah bint Ak.

Pages.Text:
Hail,

This adventurer recovered a Drudge Charm for me, and could probably help you find that drink you were looking for.
